            h3 
              span.fullScreenHoverBox Ojas wellness
        tr
          td(align='center', valign='center')
            div.hoverBox
              p Geographic gram was the first thing I ever built at a hackathon. GeoGram essintally allow's you to see user images from all over the world with a simple place's search! I learned PHP, JS, HTML5/CSS3, Google Maps API, and Instagram API! 
